  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>While based on Ryu Kan Sen, this technique is not a counter-attack, but simply a powerful offensive attack. If you are moving at a Speed Rank lower than 2, you take a -5 penalty to meet the Perform Requirements per Speed Rank you are below 2. You initiate a basic charge attack, but when you reach the target you spin rapidly and make a Kenjutsu: Iaido attack (with any charge bonuses), which deals 1d6 additional damage per 3 levels (maximum 4d6). In addition, if the target is hit it will be thrown upward 1d4 x 5 ft.<br><br>You cannot deal non-lethal damage with this technique.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The second, fourth and fifth steps grant a +1, +2 and +3 bonus (respectively) to the attack roll made for this technique.</p>\n",
